OL,3,CBody found in search for missing
OL,4,CBirmingham City fan
OL,6,FA body has been found in the search
OL,7,Ffor missing Birmingham City fan Paul
OL,8,FPike.
OL,10,FThe 18-year-old, who has autism and
OL,11,FADHD, went missing after watching
OL,12,FBirmingham City's match against Derby
OL,13,Fat Pride Park last Saturday.
OL,15,FIt's thought his last known location
OL,16,Fwas on the path near the River Derwent.
OL,18,FPolice have been searching undergrowth
OL,19,Fand have found items believed to
OL,20,Fbelong to Paul.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
