OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1774976749
OL,3,CBody found in search for missing
OL,4,CBirmingham City fan
OL,6,FOfficers discovered the body just
OL,7,Fbefore 10.30am today (Sunday, 29th
OL,8,FMarch).
OL,10,FThey say that while formal
OL,11,Fidentification has not yet taken
OL,12,Fplace, Paul's family have been made
OL,13,Faware, and they have asked that their
OL,14,Fprivacy be respected at this time.
OL,16,FThe death is not being treated as
OL,17,Fsuspicious, and there is not believed
OL,18,Fto be any third-party involvement.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
