OL,3,CBody found in search for missing
OL,4,CBirmingham City fan
OL,6,FA large number of people, from both
OL,7,Fthe local area and Paul's home city of
OL,8,FBirmingham, have been searching the
OL,9,Farea in previous days.
OL,11,FDerbyshire Police said they would like
OL,12,Fto thank them for their support during
OL,13,Fthe search.
OL,15,FA file is now being prepared for the
OL,16,Fcoroner.
